Type: PREFIX_IN_USE (prefix is being used by the origin)

CLAIM_DENIED (the claim is refused (probably          
by the origin's parent domain))

CLAIM_TO_EXPAND (origin is trying to expand           
the size of an existing prefix)
NEW_CLAIM (origin is trying to claim a new prefix)

PREFIX_MANAGED (parent is informing child of          
space available)
WITHDRAW (origin is withdrawing a previous claim)
